    dc:description "FIGURES 194–206. Thrips species. T. setosus, female 194–198: (194) Head & pronotum; (195) Antenna, right; (196) Metascutum; (197) Tergite V & pleurotergite, right side; (198) Tergites VIII–X. T. setosus, male 199–200: (199) Tergites VIII– IX; (200) Sternite VI, sculpture omitted. T. shiranesanus sp. n., female 201–206: (201) Head & pronotum; (202) Antenna, right; (203) Metascutum; (204) Tergite VI & pleurotergite, right side; (205) Tergites VIII–X; (206) Sternite VII." ;
